le_classes = ['asomething', 'bsomething']
le = preprocessing.LabelEncoder()
le.fit(le_classes)
filename = ['firstfile']
host_key = np.array(['mac1'])
tshark_srcips = np.array(["['1.1.1.1']"])
frame_epoch = None
instance = HostFootprint()
assert instance.get_individual_predictions([[0.6, 0.7]], le, filename,
    host_key, tshark_srcips, frame_epoch) == {'firstfile': [{'top_role':
    'bsomething', 'role_list': [('bsomething', 0.7), ('asomething', 0.6)],
    'source_ip': '1.1.1.1', 'source_mac': 'mac1'}]}
assert instance.get_individual_predictions([[0.2, 0.1]], le, filename,
    host_key, tshark_srcips, frame_epoch) == {'firstfile': [{'top_role':
    'Unknown', 'role_list': [('asomething', 0.2), ('bsomething', 0.1)],
    'source_ip': '1.1.1.1', 'source_mac': 'mac1'}]}
